Opposition Leader Rajoy Says No Magic Wand for Spanish Economy

-- B y   B e n   S i l l s
-- 
2011-10-08T10:35:46Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-08/opposition-leader-rajoy-says-no-magic-wand-for-spanish-economy.html
Opposition leader  Mariano Rajoy , who
is leading in polls ahead of  Spain ’s general election next
month, said there is no “magic wand” that can resolve the
problems facing the country’s economy.  “Spain will emerge from the crisis,” Rajoy told a
conference of People’s Party members in Malaga today. “It won’t
be easy. It will take time. There is no magic wand.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Ben Sills at 
 bsills@bloomberg.net  